>\n<rect x=\"20\" y=\"194\" width=\"350\" height=\"148\" fill=\"#FFFFFF\" rx=\"14\" stroke=\"#E4DDD0\" stroke-width=\"1\"/>\n<rect x=\"32\" y=\"210\" width=\"60\" height=\"20\" fill=\"#F5F0E8\" rx=\"10\"/>\n<text x=\"62\" y=\"220\" font-size=\"10\" font-weight=\"500\" font-family=\"system-ui,sans-serif\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"rgba(28,23,20,0.60)\">8:43 AM</text>\n<text x=\"32\" y=\"244\" font-size=\"16\" font-weight=\"600\" font-family=\"Georgia, serif\" fill=\"#1C1714\">On the seriality of thought —</text>\n<text x=\"32\" y=\"264\" font-size=\"16\" font-weight=\"600\" font-family=\"Georgia, serif\" fill=\"#1C1714\">how fragments cohere</text>\n<text x=\"32\" y=\"285\" font-size=\"12\" font-family=\"system-ui,sans-serif\" fill=\"rgba(28,23,20,0.60)\">There is something about returning to the same idea</text>\n<text x=\"32\" y=\"300\" font-size=\"12\" font-family=\"system-ui,sans-serif\" fill=\"rgba(28,23,20,0.60)\">across multiple sittings. Each pass reveals a new…</text>\n<rect x=\"32\" y=\"318\" width=\"88\" height=\"22\" fill=\"rgba(184,92,56,0.12)\" rx=\"11\"/>\n<text x=\"76\" y=\"325\" font-size=\"10\" font-weight=\"600\" font-family=\"system-ui,sans-serif\" text-anchor=\"middle\" letter-spacing=\"0.03em\" fill=\"#B85C38\">✦ Philosophy</text>\n<rect x=\"120\" y=\"318\" width=\"70\" height=\"22\" fill=\"#F5F0E8\" rx=\"11\"/>\n<text x=\"155\" y=\"325\" font-size=\"10\" font-weight=\"600\" font-family=\"system-ui,sans-serif\" text-anchor=\"middle\" letter-spacing=\"0.03em\" fill=\"rgba(28,23,20,0.60)\">Cognition</text>\n<text x=\"20\" y=\"362\" font-size=\"10\" font-weight=\"700\" font-family=\"system-ui,sans-serif\" letter-spacing=\"0.1em\" fill=\"rgba(28,23,20,0.35)\">RECENT</text>\n<rect x=\"20\" y=\"378\" width=\"350\" height=\"60\" fill=\"#FFFFFF\" rx=\"10\" stroke=\"#E4DDD0\" stroke-width=\"1\"/>\n<text x=\"36\" y=\"396\" font-size=\"14\" font-weight=\"500\" font-family=\"system-ui,sans-serif\" fill=\"#1C1714\">Notes on distributed attention</text>\n