t-family=\"Georgia, serif\" letter-spacing=\"-0.02em\" fill=\"#1C1714\">A Research Thread</text>\n<text x=\"20\" y=\"140\" font-size=\"12\" font-family=\"system-ui,sans-serif\" fill=\"rgba(28,23,20,0.35)\">14 notes · 6 sources · 3 syntheses</text>\n<line x1=\"20\" y1=\"158\" x2=\"370\" y2=\"158\" stroke=\"#E4DDD0\" stroke-width=\"1\"/>\n<rect x=\"20\" y=\"166\" width=\"70\" height=\"28\" fill=\"#B85C38\" rx=\"14\"/>\n<text x=\"55\" y=\"176\" font-size=\"12\" font-weight=\"600\" font-family=\"system-ui,sans-serif\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"#FFFFFF\">All</text>\n<text x=\"141\" y=\"176\" font-size=\"12\" font-weight=\"400\" font-family=\"system-ui,sans-serif\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"rgba(28,23,20,0.60)\">Notes</text>\n<text x=\"227\" y=\"176\" font-size=\"12\" font-weight=\"400\" font-family=\"system-ui,sans-serif\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"rgba(28,23,20,0.60)\">Sources</text>\n<text x=\"313\" y=\"176\" font-size=\"12\" font-weight=\"400\" font-family=\"system-ui,sans-serif\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"rgba(28,23,20,0.60)\">Synthesis</text>\n<line x1=\"30\" y1=\"208\" x2=\"30\" y2=\"332\" stroke=\"#D4C9B8\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" opacity=\"0.5\"/>\n<circle cx=\"30\" cy=\"220\" r=\"7\" fill=\"#4E7C3A\" opacity=\"0.2\"/>\n<circle cx=\"30\" cy=\"220\" r=\"4\" fill=\"#4E7C3A\"/>\n<rect x=\"48\" y=\"208\" width=\"322\" height=\"124\" fill=\"#FFFFFF\" rx=\"10\" stroke=\"#E4DDD0\" stroke-width=\"1\"/>\n<text x=\"60\" y=\"226\" font-size=\"10\" font-weight=\"500\" font-family=\"system-ui,sans-serif\" fill=\"rgba(28,23,20,0.35)\">Apr 7</text>\n<rect x=\"318\" y=\"216\" width=\"40\" height=\"22\" fill=\"#4E7C3A22\" rx=\"11\"/>\n<text x=\"338\" y=\"223\" font-size=\"10\" font-weight=\"600\" font-family=\"system-ui,sans-serif\" text-anchor=\"middle\" letter-spacing=\"0.03em\" fill=\"#4E7C3A\">Note</text>\n<text x=\"60\" y=\"246\" font-size=\"13\" font-weight=\"600\" font-family=\"system-ui,sans-serif\" fill=\"#1C1714\">Initial observation — the cost of switching</text>\n<text x=\"60\" y=\"266\" font-size=\"11\" font-family=\"system-ui,sans-serif\" fill=\"rgba(28,23,20,0.60)\">Gloria Mark's research suggests recovery time</text>\n<text x=\"60\" y=\"281\" font-size=\"11\" font-family=\"system-ui,sans-serif\" fill=\"rgba(28,23,20,0.60)\"> after interruption is ~23 minutes. But the c</text>\n<text x=\"60\" y=\"296\" font-size=\"11\" font-family=\"system-ui,sans-serif\" fill=\"rgba(28,23,20,0.60)\" opacity=\"0.8\">ost accumulates...…</text>\n<text x=\"322\" y=\"318\" font-size=\"11\" font-weight=\"600\" font-family=\"system-ui,sans-serif\" text-anchor=\"end\" fill=\"#B85C38\">Open →</text>\n<line x1=\"30\" y1=\"344\" x2=\"30\" y2=\"468\" stroke=\"#D4C9B8\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" opacity=\"0.5\"/>\n<circle cx=\"30\" cy=\"356\" r=\"7\" fill=\"#B85C38\" opacity=\"0.2\"/>\n<circle cx=\"30\" cy=\"356\" r=\"4\" fill=\"#B85C38\"/>\n<rect x=\"48\" y=\"344\" width=\"322\" height=\"124\" fill=\"#FFFFFF\" rx=\"10\" stroke=\"#E4DDD0\" stroke-width=\"1\"/>\n<text x=\"60\" y=\"362\" font-size=\"10\" font-weight=\"500\" font-family=\"system-ui,sans-serif\" fill=\"rgba(28,23,20,0.35)\">Apr 6</text>\n<rect x=\"318\" y=\"352\" width=\"52\" height=\"22\" fill=\"#B85C3822\" rx=\"11\"/>\n<text x=\"344\" y=\"359\" font-size=\"10\" font-weight=\"600\" font-family=\"system-ui,sans-serif\" text-anchor=\"middle\" letter-spacing=\"0.03em\" fill=\"#B85C38\">Source</text>\n<text x=\"60\" y=\"382\" font-size=\"13\" font-weight=\"600\" font-family=\"system-ui,sans-serif\" fill=\"#1C1714\">\"Attention and Effort\" — Kahneman, 1973</text>\n<text x=\"60\" y=\"402\" font-size=\"11\" font-family=\"system-ui,sans-serif\" fill=\"rgba(28,23,20,0.60)\">System 1 vs. System 2 framing. Effortful atte</text>\n<text x=\"60\" y=\"417\" font-size=\"11\" font-family=\"system-ui,sans-serif\" fill=\"rgba(28,23,20,0.60)\">ntion depletes reserves; low-load tasks use a</text>\n<text x=\"60\" y=\"432\" font-size=\"11\" font-family=\"system-ui,sans-serif\" fill=\"rgba(28,23,20,0.60)\" opacity=\"0.8\">mbient capacity.…</text>\n<text x=\"322\" y=\"454\" font-size=\"11\" font-weight=\"600\" font-family=\"system-ui,sans-serif\" text-anchor=\"end\" fill=\"#B85C38\">Open →</text>\n<line x1=\"30\" y1=\"480\" x2=\"30\" y2=\"604\" stroke=\"#D4C9B8\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" opacity=\"0.5\"/>\n<circle cx=\"30\" cy=\"492\" r=\"7\" fill=\"#C49A3C\" opacity=\"0.2\"/>\n<circle cx=\"30\" cy=\"492\" r=\"4\" fill=\"#C49A3C\"/>\n<rect x=\"48\" y=\"480\" width=\"322\" height=\"124\" fill=\"#FFFFFF\" rx=\"10\" stroke=\"#E4DDD0\" stroke-width=\"1\"/>\n<text x=\"60\" y=\"498\" font-size=\"10\" font-weight=\"500\" font-family=\"system-ui,sans-serif\" fill=\"rgba(28,23,20,0.35)\">Apr 5</text>\n<rect x=\"318\" y=\"488\" width=\"70\" height=\"22\" fill=\"#C49A3C22\" rx=\"11\"/>\n<text x=\"353\" y=\"495\" font-size=\"10\" font-weight=\"600\" font-family=\"system-ui,sans-serif\" text-anchor=\"middle\" letter-spacing=\"0.03em\" fill=\"#C49A3C\">Synthesis</text>\n<text x=\"60\" y=\"518\" font-size=\"13\" font-weight=\"600\" font-family=\"system-ui,sans-serif\" fill=\"#1C1714\">Synthesis: the myth of multitasking</text>\n<text x=\"60\" y=\"538\" font-size=\"11\" font-family=\"system-ui,sans-serif\" fill=\"rgba(28,23,20,0.60)\">Three studies converge on a counterintuitive </text>\n<text x=\"60\" y=\"553\" font-size=\"11\" font-family=\"system-ui,sans-serif\" fill=\"rgba(28,23,20,0.60)\">finding: distributed attention isn't lost — i</text>\n<text x=\"60\" y=\"568\" font-size=\"11\" font-family=\"system-ui,sans-serif\" fill=\"rgba(28,23,20,0.60)\" opacity=\"0.8\">t's cached...…</text>\n<text x=\"322\" y=\"590\" font-size=\"11\" font-weight=\"600\" font-family=\"system-ui,sans-serif\" text-anchor=\"end\" fill=\"#B85C38\">Open →</text>\n<line x1=\"30\" y1=\"616\" x2=\"30\" y2=\"740\" stroke=\"#D4C9B8\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" opacity=\"0.5\"/>\n<circle cx=\"30\" cy=\"628\" r=\"7\" fill=\"#4E7C3A\" opacity=\"0.2\"/>\n<circle cx=\"30\" cy=\"628\" r=\"4\" fill=\"#4E7C3A\"/>\n<rect x=\"48\" y=\"616\" width=\"322\" height=\"124\" fill=\"#FFFFFF\" rx=\"10\" stroke=\"#E4DDD0\" stroke-width=\"1\"/>\n<text x=\"60\" y=\"634\" font-size=\"10\" font-weight=\"500\" font-family=\"system-ui,sans-serif\" fill=\"rgba(28,23,20,0.35)\">Apr 4</text>\n<rect x=\"318\" y=\"624\" width=\"40\" height=\"22\" fill=\"#4E7C3A22\" rx=\"11\"/>\n<text x=\"338\" y=\"631\" font-size=\"10\" font-weight=\"600\" font-family=\"system-ui,sans-serif\" text-anchor=\"middle\" letter-spacing=\"0.03em\" fill=\"#4E7C3A\">Note</text>\n<text x=\"60\" y=\"654\" font-size=\"13\" font-weight=\"600\" font-family=\"system-ui,sans-serif\" fill=\"#1C1714\">Design implication — calm computing</text>\n<text x=\"60\" y=\"674\" font-size=\"11\" font-family=\"system-ui,sans-serif\" fill=\"rgba(28,23,20,0.60)\">Weiser's \"calm technology\" as precursor. Inte</text>\n<text x=\"60\" y=\"689\" font-size=\"11\" font-family=\"system-ui,sans-serif\" fill=\"rgba(28,23,20,0.60)\">rfaces that exist at the periphery rather tha</text>\n<text x=\"60\" y=\"704\" font-size=\"11\" font-family=\"system-ui,sans-serif\" fill=\"rgba(28,23,20,0.60)\" opacity=\"0.8\">n center...…</text>\n<text x=\"322\" y=\"726\" font-size=\"11\" font-weight=\"600\" font-family=\"system-ui,sans-serif\" text-anchor=\"end\" fill=\"#B85C38\">Open →</text>\n<rect x=\"314\" y=\"740\" width=\"56\" height=\"32\" fill=\"#B85C38\" rx=\"16\"/>\n<text x=\"342\" y=\"751\" font-size=\"12\" font-weight=\"600\" font-family=\"system-ui,sans-serif\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"#FFFFFF\">+ Add</text>\n<rect x=\"0\" y=\"780\" width=\"390\" height=\"64\" fill=\"#FBF8F3\"/>\n<line x1=\"0\" y1=\"780\" x2=\"390\" y2=\"780\" stroke=\"#E4DDD0\" stroke-width=\"1\"/>\n<rect x=\"30\" y=\"788\" width=\"40\" height=\"28\" fill=\"rgba(184,92,56,0.12)\" rx=\"8\"/>\n<circle cx=\"50\" cy=\"800\" r=\"7\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#B85C38\" stroke-width=\"1.5\"/>\n<text x=\"50\" y=\"818\" font-size=\"9\" font-weight=\"600\" font-family=\"system-ui,sans-serif\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"#B85C38\">Journal</text>\n<rect x=\"110\" y=\"788\" width=\"40\" height=\"28\" fill=\"none\" rx=\"8\"/>\n<circle cx=\"130\" cy=\"800\" r=\"7\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"rgba(28,23,20,0.60)\" stroke-width=\"1.5\"/>\n<text x=\"130\" y=\"818\" font-size=\"9\" font-weight=\"400\" font-family=\"system-ui,sans-serif\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"rgba(28,23,20,0.35)\">Search</text>\n<rect x=\"175\" y=\"788\" width=\"40\" height=\"28\" fill=\"none\" rx=\"8\"/>\n<circle cx=\"195\" cy=\"800\" r=\"7\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"rgba(28,23,20,0.60)\" stroke-width=\"1.5\"/>\n<text x=\"195\" y=\"818\" font-size=\"9\" font-weight=\"400\" font-family=\"system-ui,sans-serif\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"rgba(28,23,20,0.35)\">New</text>\n<rect x=\"240\" y=\"788\" width=\"40\" height=\"28\" fill=\"none\" rx=\"8\"/>\n<circle cx=\"260\" cy=\"800\" r=\"7\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"rgba(28,23,20,0.60)\" stroke-width=\"1.5\"/>\n<text x=\"260\" y=\"818\" font-size=\"9\" font-weight=\"400\" font-family=\"system-ui,sans-serif\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"rgba(28,23,20,0.35)\">Threads</text>\n<rect x=\"320\" y=\"788\" width=\"40\" height=\"28\" fill=\"none\" rx=\"8\"/>\n<circle cx=\"340\" cy=\"800\" r=\"7\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"rgba(28,23,20,0.60)\" stroke-width=\"1.5\"/>\n<text x=\"340\" y=\"818\" font-size=\"9\" font-weight=\"400\" font-family=\"system-ui,sans-serif\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"rgba(28,23,20,0.35)\">Library</text></svg>",
