20\" y=\"144\" font-size=\"12\" font-family=\"system-ui,sans-serif\" fill=\"rgba(28,23,20,0.60)\">Daniel Kahneman · Princeton University Press · 1973</text>\n<line x1=\"20\" y1=\"162\" x2=\"370\" y2=\"162\" stroke=\"#E4DDD0\" stroke-width=\"1\"/>\n<rect x=\"20\" y=\"170\" width=\"350\" height=\"96\" fill=\"#F5F0E8\" rx=\"12\"/>\n<rect x=\"20\" y=\"170\" width=\"4\" height=\"96\" fill=\"#B85C38\" rx=\"2\"/>\n<text x=\"32\" y=\"188\" font-size=\"10\" font-weight=\"700\" font-family=\"system-ui,sans-serif\" letter-spacing=\"0.06em\" fill=\"#B85C38\">KEY PASSAGE</text>\n<text x=\"32\" y=\"208\" font-size=\"12\" font-weight=\"400\" font-family=\"Georgia, serif\" fill=\"#1C1714\">\"Performing a task requires mental resources,</text>\n<text x=\"32\" y=\"224\" font-size=\"12\" font-weight=\"400\" font-family=\"Georgia, serif\" fill=\"#1C1714\">and the amount of effort devoted to a task is</text>\n<text x=\"32\" y=\"240\" font-size=\"12\" font-weight=\"400\" font-family=\"Georgia, serif\" fill=\"#1C1714\">itself a variable that the performer controls.\"</text>\n<text x=\"32\" y=\"258\" font-size=\"11\" font-weight=\"400\" font-family=\"system-ui,sans-serif\" fill=\"rgba(28,23,20,0.35)\">— p. 24</text>\n<text x=\"20\" y=\"282\" font-size=\"10\" font-weight=\"700\" font-family=\"system-ui,sans-serif\" letter-spacing=\"0.08em\" fill=\"rgba(28,23,20,0.35)\">YOUR NOTES (3)</text>\n<rect x=\"20\" y=\"296\" width=\"350\" height=\"56\" fill=\"#FFFFFF\" rx=\"10\" stroke=\"#E4DDD0\" stroke-width=\"1\"/>\n<circle cx=\"34\" cy=\"316\" r=\"3.5\" fill=\"#B85C38\"/>\n<text x=\"44\" y=\"314\" font-size=\"13\" font-weight=\"500\" font-family=\"system-ui,sans-serif\" fill=\"#1C1714\">On cognitive load distribution</text>\n<text x=\"44\" y=\"332\" font-size=\"11\" font-family=\"system-ui,sans-serif\" fill=\"rgba(28,23,20,0.60)\">Linked to 4 entries</text>\n<text x=\"358\" y=\"314\" font-size=\"11\" font-family=\"system-ui,sans-serif\" text-anchor=\"end\" fill=\"rgba(28,23,20,0.35)\">Apr 6</text>\n<rect x=\"20\" y=\"362\" width=\"350\" height=\"56\" fill=\"#FFFFFF\" rx=\"10\" stroke=\"#E4DDD0\" stroke-width=\"1\"/>\n<circle cx=\"34\" cy=\"382\" r=\"3.5\" fill=\"#B85C38\"/>\n<text x=\"44\" y=\"380\" font-size=\"13\" font-weight=\"500\" font-family=\"system-ui,sans-serif\" fill=\"#1C1714\">Dual-task paradigm — implications</text>\n<text x=\"44\" y=\"398\" font-size=\"11\" font-family=\"system-ui,sans-serif\" fill=\"rgba(28,23,20,0.60)\">Linked to 2 entries</text>\n<text x=\"358\" y=\"380\" font-size=\"11\" font-family=\"system-ui,sans-serif\" text-anchor=\"end\" fill=\"rgba(28,23,20,0.35)\">Apr 5</text>\n<rect x=\"20\" y=\"428\" width=\"350\" height=\"56\" fill=\"#FFFFFF\" rx=\"10\" stroke=\"#E4DDD0\" stroke-width=\"1\"/>\n<circle cx=\"34\" cy=\"448\" r=\"3.5\" fill=\"#B85C38\"/>\n<text x=\"44\" y=\"446\" font-size=\"13\" font-weight=\"500\" font-family=\"system-ui,sans-serif\" fill=\"#1C1714\">Arousal vs. mental load distinction</text>\n<text x=\"44\" y=\"464\" font-size=\"11\" font-family=\"system-ui,sans-serif\" fill=\"rgba(28,23,20,0.60)\">New note</text>\n<text x=\"358\" y=\"446\" font-size=\"11\" font-family=\"system-ui,sans-serif\" text-anchor=\"end\" fill=\"rgba(28,23,20,0.35)\">Apr 4</text>\n<text x=\"20\" y=\"498\" font-size=\"10\" font-weight=\"700\" font-family=\"system-ui,sans-serif\" letter-spacing=\"0.08em\" fill=\"rgba(28,23,20,0.35)\">RELATED SOURCES (2)</text>\n<rect x=\"20\" y=\"512\" width=\"350\" height=\"54\" fill=\"#FFFFFF\" rx=\"10\" stroke=\"#E4DDD0\" stroke-width=\"1\"/>\n<rect x=\"32\" y=\"521\" width=\"40\" height=\"22\" fill=\"#F5F0E8\" rx=\"11\"/>\n<text x=\"52\" y=\"528\" font-size=\"10\" font-weight=\"600\" font-family=\"system-ui,sans-serif\" text-anchor=\"middle\" letter-spacing=\"0.03em\" fill=\"rgba(28,23,20,0.35)\">BOOK</text>\n<text x=\"86\" y=\"530\" font-size=\"13\" font-weight=\"500\" font-family=\"system-ui,sans-serif\" fill=\"#1C1714\">Flow: Psychology of Optimal Experience</text>\n<text x=\"86\" y=\"548\" font-size=\"11\" font-family=\"system-ui,sans-serif\" fill=\"rgba(28,23,20,0.60)\">Csikszentmihalyi · 1990</text>\n<text x=\"358\" y=\"539\" font-size=\"14\" font-weight=\"600\" font-family=\"system-ui,sans-serif\" text-anchor=\"end\" fill=\"#B85C38\">→</text>\n<rect x=\"20\" y=\"576\" width=\"350\" height=\"54\" fill=\"#FFFFFF\" rx=\"10\" stroke=\"#E4DDD0\" stroke-width=\"1\"/>\n<rect x=\"32\" y=\"585\" width=\"40\" height=\"22\" fill=\"#F5F0E8\" rx=\"11\"/>\n<text x=\"52\" y=\"592\" font-size=\"10\" font-weight=\"600\" font-family=\"system-ui,sans-serif\" text-anchor=\"middle\" letter-spacing=\"0.03em\" fill=\"rgba(28,23,20,0.35)\">BOOK</text>\n<text x=\"86\" y=\"594\" font-size=\"13\" font-weight=\"500\" font-family=\"system-ui,sans-serif\" fill=\"#1C1714\">The Shallows</text>\n<text x=\"86\" y=\"612\" font-size=\"11\" font-family=\"system-ui,sans-serif\" fill=\"rgba(28,23,20,0.60)\">Nicholas Carr · 2010</text>\n<text x=\"358\" y=\"603\" font-size=\"14\" font-weight=\"600\" font-family=\"system-ui,sans-serif\" text-anchor=\"end\" fill=\"#B85C38\">→</text>\n<rect x=\"20\" y=\"648\" width=\"350\" height=\"52\" fill=\"#1C1714\" rx=\"12\"/>\n<text x=\"195\" y=\"666\" font-size=\"14\" font-weight=\"600\" font-family=\"system-ui,sans-serif\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"#FFFFFF\">✦ Synthesize with CARTE AI</text>\n<text x=\"195\" y=\"684\" font-size=\"11\" font-family=\"system-ui,sans-serif\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"rgba(255,255,255,0.55)\">Generate insights from all notes on this source</text>\n<rect x=\"20\" y=\"710\" width=\"171\" height=\"40\" fill=\"#F5F0E8\" rx=\"10\"/>\n<rect x=\"199\" y=\"710\" width=\"171\" height=\"40\" fill=\"#F5F0E8\" rx=\"10\"/>\n<text x=\"105.5\" y=\"724\" font-size=\"12\" font-weight=\"500\" font-family=\"system-ui,sans-serif\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"rgba(28,23,20,0.60)\">Copy Citation</text>\n<text x=\"284.5\" y=\"724\" font-size=\"12\" font-weight=\"500\" font-family=\"system-ui,sans-serif\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"rgba(28,